Leon Trefler is Senior Vice President of Global Customer Success. In this role, he oversees Sales and Consulting for the Americas as well as Global Alliances.
Leon has held key management positions with increasing responsibility across the organization during his 16 years with Pega. These titles include Head of Global Sales, and, previously, Vice President of Sales for North America. In 2002, he launched the commercialization of Pegasystems’ flagship BPM solution. He started at Pega in 1998 as an account executive for strategic business development.
Leon holds a B.A. degree from Dartmouth College.



